{"title":"秋罗寨（外二首）","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":7,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋罗寨（外二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席在秋罗寨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住的那平房几间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是在长征的路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是在草地的边缘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前就是草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前就是胜利。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前，向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党在这里决定了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前，向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军不怕远征难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士胸中的热血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似烈火一团团。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军已把四座雪山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧起来作火把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧掉祖国的枷锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民身上的铁链。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征长征向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗在前面召唤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征好比播种机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播下革命的种子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大渡河上的枪声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破铁壁合围。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁索桥上的火把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破群山的黑暗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征是伟大的宣言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣告中国的黎明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火是笔写在雪山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绘出万里画卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一页是在井冈山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后一页在延安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——1949年的回忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西柏坡上一棵巨松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擂响了震天的宏钟（注），"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山谷轰鸣长缨飘动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看红旗已盖上天空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座古老的白塔上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞来了这万里征鸿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让火花照亮了天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着钟声走进花丛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）西柏坡是党中央进北"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"京以前住的地方，在河北"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"省平山县滹沱河岸上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一个历史故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一每当我看见枣树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就想起白毛女；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她那白的头发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似一座大雪山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命带来了星火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣树挂上红果；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她把这红果吞下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变得像一支火炬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二钟声唤醒白毛女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火融化了冰柱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白毛女走出山洞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔向红色的天宇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像火炬在急奔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像火人在狂呼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手臂高举作利斧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身子挺立像枣树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三白毛女呵白毛女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山林已由你作主；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晋察冀大山的主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是这坚实的枣树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瀑布是你的歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣林是你的门户；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青的花呀红的果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你绣的红枣图。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}